
                                           Data Types
                                               |
                         -----------------------------------------------------------
             Primitive                                                             Non-primitive
               |                                                                       |
       Boolean              numeric Type                                      String, Array, etc....
                                  |
         |           Character          Integral Value
                        |
       boolean       char                    |
                                   Integer         floating
                                     |                 |
                       byte short  int long        float double


Boolean:
     it can have two values, true/false. the size of boolean depends on virtual machine.
     the default value for boolean is 'false'.

Byte:

    Data Type        syntax                 size                       value                       default value
    boolean       boolean booleanVar       Virtual Machine specific    true/false                   false
     byte         byte byteVar              8 bits                      -2pow7 to 2pow7              0
     short        short shortVar            16 bits                     -2pow15 to 2pow15            0
     int          int intvar                32bits                      -2pow31 to 2pow31            0
     long         long longVal              64bit                       -2pow63 to 2pow63            0

Assessment:
   -> Continue the data type program, with int and log datatypes.


1024 bits - 1kb
1024kb - 1 mb
1024 mb - 1gb
